For the 2000/01 marketing year:
(a) the minimum price referred to in Article 3 of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 shall be EUR 87,886 per 100 kg net from the producer for unprocessed dried figs;
(b) the production aid referred to in Article 4 of that Regulation shall be EUR 28,63 per 100 kg net for dried figs.
